%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edoctors%20who%20specialize%20in%20geriatric%20care%20is%20also%20dwindling%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20even%20as%20populations%20age.%20Medical%20professionals%20told%20BI%20in%20March%20the%20influx%20of%20older%20patients%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20quality-of-care%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20ease%20burnout%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-tech-innovations-help-medical-billing-diagnostics-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthcare-focused%20AI%20startups%20have%20raised%20billions%20by%20pitching%20themselves%20as%20the%20fix%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Startups%20like%20Suki%2C%20Zephyr%20AI%2C%20and%20Tennr%20say%20they%20can%20lighten%20workload%20by%20automating%20repetitive%20tasks%20like%20billing%20and%20note-taking%2C%20improving%20diagnosis%20accuracy%2C%20and%20identifying%20patients%20for%20emerging%20treatments%2C%20Business%20Insider%20reported%20in%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20consulting%20firm%20McKinsey%20estimates%20that%20generative%20AI%20could%20boost%20productivity%20in%20healthcare%20and%20pharma%20by%20up%20to%20%24370%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEducation%20is%20headed%20in%20the%20same%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20according%20to%20federal%20data%20released%20in%202023%2C%2086%25%20of%20K-12%20public%20schools%20reported%20difficulties%20hiring%20teachers%20for%20the%202023-24%20school%20year.%20About%2045%25%20of%20public%20schools%20said%20they%20were%20understaffed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20UK%2C%20a%20London%20high%20school%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-ai-tools-replace-teachers-high-school-students-learning-education-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereplacing%20some%20teachers%20with%20AI%20tools%20like%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20students%20prep%20for%20exams%2C%20BI%20reported%20last%20year.%20The%20pilot%20program%20at%20David%20Game%20College%20involved%2020%20students%20using%20AI%20tools%20for%20a%20year%20in%20core%20subjects%20such%20as%20English%2C%20math%2C%20biology%2C%20and%20computer%20science.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20concerns%20about%20students%20using%20AI%20to%20cheat%2C%20educators%20told%20BI%20last%20year%20they're%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-in-the-classroom-has-some-people-worried-teachers-arent-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoptimistic%20about%20generative%20AI's%20potential%20to%20save%20teachers%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20improve%20learning%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20as%20classrooms%20become%20harder%20to%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227e160770-d38d-4f3e-8d90-351836f49f35%5C%22%3EIf%20AI%20does%20the%20jobs%2C%20what's%20left%20for%20humans%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGates%20wasn't%20just%20talking%20about%20teachers%20and%20doctors.%20He%20also%20said%20AI%20was%20coming%20for%20factory%20workers%2C%20construction%20crews%2C%20and%20hotel%20cleaners%20%E2%80%94%20anyone%20doing%20work%20that%20required%20physical%20skill%20and%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20hands%20have%20to%20be%20awfully%20good%20to%20do%20those%20things.%20We'll%20achieve%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETech%20giants%20like%20Nvidia%20are%20betting%20big%20on%20humanoid%20robots%20designed%20to%20perform%20manual%20tasks%2C%20from%20picking%20items%20in%20warehouses%20to%20scrubbing%20floors.%20These%20robots%20aim%20to%20reduce%20labor%20costs%20and%20boost%20efficiency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGates%20said%20the%20world%20is%20heading%20toward%20a%20future%20where%20work%20could%20be%20drastically%20reduced%20%E2%80%94%20or%20at%20least%20looks%20very%20different%20from%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20retire%20early%2C%20you%20can%20work%20shorter%20workweeks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20require%20almost%20a%20philosophical%20rethink%20about%2C%20'Okay%2C%20how%20should%20time%20be%20spent%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGates%20admits%20he's%20also%20grappling%20with%20that%20question.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20hard%20for%20those%20of%20us%20%E2%80%94%20in%20my%20case%2C%20spending%20almost%2070%20years%20in%20a%20world%20of%20shortage%20%E2%80%94%20even%20to%20adjust%20my%20mind%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201930%2C%20economist%20John%20Maynard%20Keynes%20predicted%20that%20technological%20advances%20could%20eventually%20reduce%20the%20workweek%20to%20just%2015%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%20a%20century%20later%2C%20despite%20major%20productivity%20leaps%2C%20most%20people%20still%20work%20around%2040%20hours%20weekly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20have%20to%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Gates%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20choose%20to%20work.%20Because%3F%20Because%20it's%20fun.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-gates-ai-job-shortages-doctors-teachers-work-free-time-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744782426000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ff3fdaa466d2b74ab3467d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-gates-ai-job-shortages-doctors-teachers-work-free-time-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20billionaire%20said%20tech%20will%20help%20plug%20labor%20gaps%2C%20even%20in%20blue-collar%20roles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cmlee%40insider.com%20(Lee%20Chong%20Ming)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-gates-ai-job-shortages-doctors-teachers-work-free-time-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Former%20T-ara%20member%20Ahreum%20sentenced%20to%206%20months%20prison%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744782166000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-120332399%2Cimgsize-15066.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesof