icalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsahara-groups-aamby-valley-land-worth-rs-1-460-crore-seized-8174698%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22David's%20Bridal%20CEO%20says%20the%20company%20raced%20to%20avoid%20price%20hikes%20over%20tariffs%20by%20shifting%20dress%20production%20out%20of%20China%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22David's%20Bridal%20store%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67feed153fe8d39283632bbd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20CEO%20of%20David's%20Bridal%20said%20the%20company%20started%20moving%20production%20out%20of%20China%20months%20ago.%3Cp%3EPaul%20Weaver%2FSOPA%20Images%2FLightRocket%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDavid's%20Bridal%20shifted%20production%20from%20China%20to%20avoid%20tariffs%2C%20CEO%20Kelly%20Cook%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company%20reduced%20China-based%20production%20from%20over%2050%25%20to%20about%2030%25%20in%20recent%20months.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDavid's%20Bridal%20is%20also%20exploring%20the%20feasibility%20of%20producing%20wedding%20dresses%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20largest%20bridal%20retailer%20in%20the%20US%20started%20shifting%20its%20production%20out%20of%20China%20months%20ago%20in%20anticipation%20of%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavids-bridal-history-from-founding-to-bankruptcy-layoffs-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDavid's%20Bridal%20%3C%2Fa%3ECEO%20Kelly%20Cook%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20company%20was%20not%20%26quot%3Btariff-proof%26quot%3B%20but%20%26quot%3Btariff-resilient%26quot%3B%20going%20into%20April%2C%20when%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20latest%20tariff%20push%20sent%20companies%20around%20the%20world%20scrambling%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnyse-photos-trump-tariffs-reactions-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinancial%20markets%20tanking%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECook%2C%20who%20took%20over%20as%20CEO%20on%20April%201%2C%20said%20the%20company%20has%2036%20design%20and%20production%20facilities%20around%20the%20world%2C%20including%20in%20China%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Vietnam%2C%20the%20Philippines%2C%20Myanmar%2C%20and%20India.%20That%20diversified%20production%20allowed%20the%20company%20to%20proactively%20respond%20to%20potential%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump%3C%2Fa%3E%20announced%20a%20145%25%20tariff%20on%20goods%20from%20China%20last%20week%2C%20the%20company%20had%20already%20largely%20shifted%20production%20to%20its%20facilities%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECook%20said%20that%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months%20the%20company%20decreased%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwinners-and-losers-trump-tariff-pause-stock-prices-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChina%3C%2Fa%3E-based%20production%20from%20over%2050%25%20of%20its%20total%20to%20about%2030%25%2C%20a%20move%20that%20was%20possible%20due%20to%20the%20production%20that%20was%20already%20ongoing%20in%20other%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20do%20everything%20in%20our%20power%20not%20to%20pass%20anything%20on%20to%20the%20customer%2C%26quot%3B%20Cook%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20as%20of%20last%20week%2C%20David's%20Bridal%20had%20not%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-dynamic-pricing-inflation-costs-china-trade-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraised%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20result%20of%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20majority%20of%20bridal%20gowns%20sold%20in%20the%20US%20are%20produced%20in%20China%2C%20making%20the%20industry%20highly%20susceptible%20to%20the%20impacts%20of%20Trump's%20trade%20war.%20Independent%20bridal%20shops%20recently%20told%20BI%20that%20about%2090%25%20of%20their%20gowns%20were%20made%20in%20China%20and%20that%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20wholesale%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftariffs-trump-china-wedding-dresses-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewedding%20dress%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20already%20rising%20as%20a%20result%20of%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20wedding%20dress%20sold%20in%20the%20US%20retails%20for%20around%20%242%2C000%20according%20to%20wedding%20planning%20website%20The%20Knot%2C%20so%20the%20steep%20tariffs%20on%20China%20could%20result%20in%20brides%20or%20bridal%20shops%20being%20hit%20with%20a%20hefty%20additional%20cost.%20And%20for%20couples%20getting%20married%2C%20that%20increase%20would%20be%20on%20top%20of%20the%20average%20cost%20of%20a%20wedding%20in%20the%20US%2C%20which%20The%20Knot%20puts%20at%20%2433%2C000.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20moving%20its%20own%20production%20out%20of%20China%2C%20David's%20Bridal%20is%20also%20helping%20some%20of%20the%20manufacturers%20it%20partners%20with%20move%20their%20operations%20out%20of%20the%20country%20and%20to%20some%20of%20its%20other%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECook%20said%20the%20company%20also%20has%20about%20300%2C000%20gowns%20already%20state-side%20in%20its%20193%20stores%20located%20throughout%20the%20US%2C%20so%20they%20wouldn't%20be%20subject%20to%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20very%20focused%20on%20ensuring%20that%20that%20level%20of%20inventory%20stays%20voluminous%20so%20we%20can%20anticipate%20needs%20like%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECook%20added%20that%20with%20so%20much%20uncertainty%20around%20tariffs%2C%20David's%20Bridal%20is%20focusing%20on%20the%20factors%20it%20can%20control%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Boptimizing%2C%20looking%20at%20cost%20controls%2C%20moving%20production%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe'll%20just%20continue%20to%20stay%20focused%20on%20that%20until%20the%20dust%20settles%20on%20all%20of%20the%20tariffs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavid's%20Bridal%20is%20also%20exploring%20the%20possibility%20of%20producing%20gowns%20in%20the%20US.%20Cook%20said%20the%20company%20is%20visiting%20a%20potential%20manufacturing%20location%20in%20June%20to%20evaluate%20if%20production%20could%20occur%20stateside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Bridal%20Retailers%20Association%2C%20which%20represents%20about%206%2C000%20independent%20bridal%20shops%2C%20recently%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20US%20does%20not%20currently%20have%20the%20infrastructure%20to%20produce%20the%20quality%20of%20dresses%20at%20scale%20that%20can%20be%20produced%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20doubt%20that%20we%20can%20find%20the%20labor%20and%20the%20talent%20in%20the%20US%20to%20do%20the%20same%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20Cook%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20about%20timing%20and%20location%20and%20other%20economic%20factors%20like%20capital%20and%20so%20forth%20that%20we%20will%20evaluate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavids-bridal-ceo-wedding-dress-production-china-tariffs-raising-prices-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744765486000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67feee77a466d2b74ab344a0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavids-bridal-ceo-wedding-dress-production-china-tariffs-raising-prices-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kelly%20Cook%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20David's%20Bridal%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20company%20started%20moving%20dress%20production%20out%20of%20China%20months%20ago.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kvlamis%40businessinsider.com%20(Kelsey%20Vlamis)%22%2C