she%20was%20so%20sick.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Kochan%20recounted%20her%20latest%20hook-ups%20to%20Boyer%20that%20day%2C%20the%20two%20began%20joking%20that%20it%20would%20make%20a%20great%20TV%20show.%20From%20there%2C%20they%20pitched%20it%20around%2C%20eventually%20scoring%20a%20podcast%20deal%20with%20Wondery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20podcast%2C%20which%20debuted%20in%20early%202020%20after%20Kochan's%20death%2C%20amassed%20a%20loyal%20fan%20base%2C%20thanks%20in%20part%20to%20her%20no-holds-barred%20approach%20to%20her%20sexual%20encounters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20are%20you%20going%20to%20do%20to%20me%3F%20Kill%20me%3F%20I'm%20dying%2C%26quot%3B%20Kochan%20joked%20on%20one%20episode%20of%20the%20six-part%20podcast%20in%20response%20to%20concern%20about%20going%20home%20with%20strangers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22013a799f-02ac-49f2-9b1e-5f2933226850%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20series%20makes%20changes%20to%20the%20real%20Molly's%20story%2C%20but%20stays%20true%20to%20its%20heart%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Michelle%20Williams%20in%20%26quot%3BDying%20For%20Sex.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f288db5d203112923e3585%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMichelle%20Williams%20in%20%26quot%3BDying%20For%20Sex.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EFX%2FHulu%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20series%20is%20mostly%20faithful%20to%20Kochan's%20real%20story%2C%20creators%20Elizabeth%20Meriwether%20and%20Kim%20Rosenstock%20made%20a%20few%20changes%20to%20adapt%20it%20for%20television.%20For%20instance%2C%20Kochan's%20husband's%20name%20and%20profession%20have%20been%20changed%20out%20of%20respect%20for%20his%20privacy%2C%20according%20to%20Boyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20series%20also%20condensed%20several%20men%20that%20Kochan%20dated%20into%20one%20character%2C%20simply%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BNeighbor%20Guy%26quot%3B%20(Rob%20Delaney)%2C%20with%20whom%20the%20character%20explores%20a%20variety%20of%20kinks%20and%20fetishes%20and%20ends%20up%20having%20a%20mutually%20fulfilling%20sexual%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20real%20Kochan%20didn't%20end%20up%20breaking%20her%20femur%20while%20acquiescing%20his%20request%20to%20kick%20him%20in%20the%20groin%2C%20as%20the%20show%20depicts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoyer%20added%20that%20there%20were%20also%20some%20timeline%20changes%2C%20which%20helped%20to%20raise%20the%20stakes%20dramatically.%20For%20instance%2C%20in%20real%20life%2C%20Boyer%20was%20well%20into%20her%20relationship%20with%20her%20boyfriend%20before%20Molly%20got%20sick%2C%20so%20her%20love%20life%20wasn't%20nearly%20as%20tumultuous%20as%20what's%20depicted%20on%20screen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20changes%20to%20me%20felt%20very%20in%20line%20with%20this%20version%20of%20the%20story%2C%26quot%3B%20Boyer%20said.%20%26quot%3BAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20Molly%20and%20I%20very%20much%20feel%20like%20the%20center%2C%20so%20the%20changes%20don't%20really%20bother%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2262f577f8-10e7-44db-928b-959b99709341%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMichelle%20Williams%20and%20Jenny%20Slate%20said%20they%20made%20the%20characters%20their%20own%20instead%20of%20copies%20of%20the%20real%20Molly%20Kochan%20and%20Nikki%20Boyer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jenny%20Slate%20and%20Michelle%20Williams%20in%20%26quot%3BDying%20For%20Sex.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f2884eb8b41a9673fcc605%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJenny%20Slate%20and%20Michelle%20Williams%20in%20%26quot%3BDying%20For%20Sex.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EFX%2FHulu%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAmid%20an%20increasingly%20popular%20trend%20of%20adapting%20narrative%20and%20non-fiction%20podcasts%20