0the%20material%20combines%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352270%2Fsustainable-home-in-maharashtra-naturally-cool-summers-mango-trees-shriya-parasrampuria-prashant-dupare%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elow%20maintenance%20and%20sustainability%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20bringing%20a%20biophilic%20touch%20to%20interiors.%20The%20%E2%80%98walls%E2%80%99%2C%20they%20add%2C%20require%20no%20watering%20or%20sunlight.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20customisable%20and%20eco-friendly%2C%20offering%20functional%20and%20aesthetic%20benefits%20ideal%20for%20modern%20interior%20spaces.%E2%80%9D%20One%20of%20the%20biggest%20boons%20is%20their%20acoustic%20properties.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMitu%20points%20out%2C%20%E2%80%9CMoss%20walls%20absorb%20sound%20and%20reduce%20noise%20reverberation%2C%20creating%20quieter%20and%20more%20comfortable%20indoor%20environments.%20They%20are%20particularly%20effective%20in%20open-plan%20offices%20where%20sound%20control%20is%20a%20priority.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsustainable-architecture-1744381698.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Moss%20walls%20require%20little%20maintenance%20and%20upkeep%20and%20act%20as%20great%20air%20purifiers%20to%20filter%20out%20volatile%20organic%20compounds%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsustainable-architecture-1744381698.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsustainable-architecture-1744381698-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsustainable-architecture-1744381698-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsus